belongsTo
We
've set up two models - User and Order - and told them about each other. You can set up as many associations on\neach Model as you need using the two default types - <a href=\"#/api/Ext.data.HasManyAssociation\" rel=\"Ext.data.HasManyAssociation\" class=\"docClass\">hasMany</a> and\n<a href=\"#/api/Ext.data.BelongsToAssociation\" rel=\"Ext.data.BelongsToAssociation\" class=\"docClass\">belongsTo</a>.
